title: Mangalvaar
subTitle: While investigating mysterious suicides in a village, Maaya, the sub-inspector of police, realises that they are murders in reality.

title: The Reunion
subTitle: Long after high school, Ricky has embraced a spiritual lifestyle. But when his childhood nemesis, Travis, is at their reunion, he sets off on a nightmarish journey of confrontation.

title: Bhoot Returns
subTitle: Tarun and Namrata move into a luxurious bungalow with Taman and Nimmi, their son and daughter respectively. However, strange occurrences start taking place and they must escape in order to survive.

title: Kismat
subTitle: Tony, a hitman, unwittingly puts the father of the girl he loves in deep trouble. He realises his blunder and sets out to put things straight, but it might be too late.

title: Jai Shree Ganesh
subTitle: Revered as the god of good luck, Lord Ganesh returns to the world to grant good fortune to the living and relieve pain and misery among devotees.

title: Runway 34
subTitle: Upon dealing with the rough climate in Cochin, two pilots make a risky landing in Thiruvananthapuram. But trouble ensues when personnel from the AAIB probes the matter.

title: Krack
subTitle: Three delinquents attempt to outwit a resolute police officer, underestimating his clever methods and unwavering dedication to law enforcement.

title: Players
subTitle: A master thief stumbles upon a secret lead about a shipment of gold ingots being transported from Russia to Romania. Eventually, he recruits a gang of sly criminals to stage a daring heist.

title: I
subTitle: A bodybuilder and successful model plans revenge after his enemies inject him with a substance that deforms his body.

title: Khoonkhaar
subTitle: Gagan, a brave young man, is unable to be with Sweety, his true love, due to her parents' disapproval of him. However, he vows to protect her after unknowingly saving her from gangsters.

title: Krantiveer
subTitle: Pratap, a gambler disowned by his family, comes under the care of a landlord named Laxminath. When corrupt forces lead to Laxminath's murder, Pratap seeks revenge.

title: Aparichit - The Stranger
subTitle: A meek lawyer, frustrated with his inability to change the system, develops a vigilante alter-ego to mete out justice to criminals. However, the police soon set out to track down the vigilante.

title: Aparichit - The Stranger
subTitle: A meek lawyer, frustrated with his inability to change the system, develops a vigilante alter-ego to mete out justice to criminals. However, the police soon set out to track down the vigilante.

title: Goodbye, Butterfly
subTitle: Suspicion turns to obsession when a man starts to think that an oddball neighbor killed a 5-year-old girl.

title: Blurr
subTitle: Suspicious about the circumstances surrounding her twin sister's death, a woman with progressive blindness searches for answers that eventually lead her down a dangerous path.

title: Flight
subTitle: Multimillionaire Ranveer Malhotra goes against all odds and takes on life-threatening obstacles in a bid to survive on an aeroplane after his manufacturing company deals with a massive fiasco.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Bawaal
subTitle: A small-town man falls in love with the prettiest girl in town. However, he ends up marrying her in order to raise his social standing.

title: Time Story
subTitle: Sethuraman, a scientist, invents a time-travelling gadget that his evil twin Athreya wants to get hold of. Soon, a bitter battle arises between Sethuraman's son and Athreya.

title: Vijay The Master
subTitle: Troubled alcoholic teacher JD goes to work at a juvenile reform school. When he realises a dangerous criminal is using students to cover up his crimes, JD sets out to stop him.

title: Surya The Soldier
subTitle: When a soldier lands in trouble due to his anger issues, he begins seeing a psychologist in hopes of one day returning to duty.

title: Makkhi
subTitle: After reincarnating as a fly, a murderer decides to take revenge on his rival, who killed him, and teams up with a woman to destroy the killer's life.

title: Dhamaal
subTitle: Four lazy friends learn about a hidden treasure in Goa and set out to find it. However, a police inspector learns about their plan and begins to pursue them.

title: Enemy
subTitle: Rajiv grows envious of his childhood friend, Chozhan, as he is better than him at most things. The frenemies grow apart only to meet under very different circumstances several years later.

title: Enemy
subTitle: Rajiv grows envious of his childhood friend, Chozhan, as he is better than him at most things. The frenemies grow apart only to meet under very different circumstances several years later.

title: Vicky Donor
subTitle: Vicky, a lively young man, works as a sperm donor for Dr Baldev Chaddha and proves to be highly successful. Consequently, Baldev's clinic thrives with the help of Vicky's contributions.

title: Namaste England
subTitle: Param and Jasmeet fall in love and get married. However, things get complicated when Jasmeet wishes to relocate to London and establish her career.

title: The Dunes
subTitle: When a journalist moves to his hometown, he does not have the slightest idea that the strings of his unresolved past are lying there in wait to entangle him in a psychological Gordian knot.

title: Race
subTitle: The relationship between two stepbrothers develops cracks when they fall in love with the same woman. As a result, the younger brother tries to kill the other and inherit the insurance money.

title: Radhe Shyam
subTitle: Despite being a doctor with no inclination towards superstitious beliefs, Prerana places her love and faith in Aditya, a palmist whose predictions turn out to be too spot-on to be disregarded.

title: Kisi Ka Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan
subTitle: Bhaijaan, the eldest of three siblings, refuses to get married to maintain harmony in his family. However, complications arise after his brothers conspire for him to fall in love.

title: Baby John
subTitle: An indomitable policeman goes to greater lengths and leads a double life in order to protect his daughter from the criminal underworld.

title: Businessman 2
subTitle: A money-minded tycoon gets into a beneficial relationship with a woman. Soon, he learns about the differences in his family and decides to end them.

title: Jai Ho
subTitle: A former Indian military officer devises a unique plan to promote social responsibility amongst apathetic civilians. The masses embrace his initiative, but he must confront a potent political family.

title: Koogle Kuttappa
subTitle: A conservative villager hates the idea of his son relocating to Russia for a job. However, when his son brings a robot to care for him, he develops an unlikely bond with the machine.
